YEAH, I MEAN, ALL THE
RESOURCES WE UTILIZE

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.000
AS A SPECIES COMES
FROM PLANET EARTH.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.000
WE DON'T, YOU KNOW,
MINE ASTEROIDS;

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:21.000
WE DON'T GO TO JUPITER FOR
OUR HYDROGEN AND HELIUM.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:24.000
EVERYTHING WE GET, WE GET
FROM THE CRUST OF THE EARTH.

