ALL THE MINIMAL RESOURCES
THAT WE USE FOR METALS

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:30.000
AND THE STEEL IN BUILDINGS,
THE GLASS WE HAVE

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:34.000
IN SKY SCRAPERS, THIS
