EVEN THE MOST HIGH
TECH PLASTIC, YOU KNOW,

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:41.000
COMPUTER PART OR TOY OR
WHAT HAVE YOU, THESE ARE

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:45.000
RAW MATERIALS THAT WE
HAVE TO SURVEY, WE HAVE TO

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:48.000
IDENTIFY, AND WE HAVE
TO RESPONSIBLY EXPLOIT

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:51.000
FROM THE EARTH IN
ORDER TO MAINTAIN

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:54.000
THE TYPE OF CIVILIZATION
WE HAVE TODAY.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
OUR FAST-PACED,
TECHNOLOGICAL,

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.000
CONSUMER-BASED AND EVER
GROWING CIVILIZATION RELIES

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.000
HEAVILY ON THE NATURAL
RESOURCES FROM THE EARTH.

