AND AS THE POPULATION
GROWS, THE DEMAND GROWS,

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.000
AND AS A RESULT
WE ARE IN DANGER

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:12.000
OF DEPLETING THESE
NATURAL RESOURCES.

