HUMAN ACTIVITIES ARE ALSO
HAVING TREMENDOUS IMPACTS

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:22.000
ON THE OCEANS, ON THE SOILS
OF THE EARTH, ON ITS FORESTS.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:25.000
WE'RE CUTTING DOWN
TREES; THE OCEAN IS THE

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:28.000
CLASSIC EXAMPLE, WE'RE JUST
OVER FISHING THE OCEAN.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:31.000
THE NEED FOR FOOD,
ENERGY AND MATERIALS

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.000
IS GROWING AT AN
ASTOUNDING RATE.

