THE FUELS FOR CARS AND
INDUSTRIES IS POLLUTING

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.000
OUR AIR WITH
SMOG AND ACID RAIN,

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:46.000
AND MANY OF THE
MATERIALS WE USE

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:49.000
END UP AS WASTE,
FILLING UP LANDFILLS.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:52.000
WE ARE POLLUTING THE
OCEANS WITH GAS AND OIL,

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:54.000
CONTAMINATING OUR FRESH
WATER WITH PESTICIDES

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.000
AND SEWAGE... AND THE
LIST IS GROWING.

