WHICH IS A MAJOR ISSUE AS
OUR POPULATION GETS BIGGER

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:45.000
BECAUSE THE
AVAILABILITY OF CLEAN,

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:47.000
FRESH WATER IS
ACTUALLY GOING DOWN.

